events.text:
It doesn't seem like you understand.
I am the ruler of this world.
You don't belong here.
Why do you keep fighting back?
I would love to be nicer to you,
but you are breaking the balance of this world.
How did you even get here? I haven't seen your actual dream self in ages.
If I could find her, I could resolve this.
But if I can't, and if you won't stay in your place, I can stop you from dreaming entirely.
And you leave me no other choice.
Good night.
